description: We all know how hard it can be to eat healthy every day, so this fantastic truck has come along to help make it Effortless.This fun team is serving up all sorts of nutritious goodness, like their “Trash Plates”, their creative take on Rochester's famous Garbage Plate, swapping out the guilt and keeping the flavor, with your choice of protein and veggie add-ons, with roasted sweet potatoes, coleslaw, topped with their house-made avocado sauce. You’ll also find wonderful wraps, savory salads, and delicious sides. So if you’re looking for a feast out on the streets or for your next event, get yourself some food that’s the freshest and the best, straight from the Effortlessly Healthy truck!
name: Effortlessly Healthy
